    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><dateline><placeName ref="pl0001">Downing</placeName> July 13<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>. 1781.</dateline><salute>Dear
                    Sir</salute></opener>
                <p>The plague of attendance on the military government called militia has so
                    engrossed me that I could not attend sooner to <choice>
                        <abbr>y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi></abbr>
                        <expan>your</expan>
                    </choice> most obliging favor. my best thanks attend Miss Bulls<note type="editorial"><persName ref="pe0331">Elizabeth</persName> and <persName ref="pe0336">Catherine Bull</persName>, and, possibly, <persName ref="pe0346">Levinia Luther</persName>.</note> for their useful
                    communication:<note type="editorial">A direct communication from Bull's
                        daughters, Elizabeth and Catherine, regarding techniques of
                        extra-illustration is suggested here, but it does not appear to have
                        survived.</note><persName ref="pe0238"> M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi> Pennant</persName> freely entrusts me to the tuition of 
                            <abbr>y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi></abbr>
                            <expan>your</expan>
                        fair daughters &amp; I hope to profit by their lessons. </p>
                <p><persName ref="pe0014">Moses</persName> is now on the point of becoming
                    an absolute housekeeper &amp; to work on his own account unless when employed by
                    me. he charges for the drawing of </p>
                <p>
                    <table>
                        <row role="data">
                            <cell role="data"> </cell>
                            <cell role="data"> </cell>
                            <cell role="data">s</cell>
                            <cell role="data"/>
                        </row>
                        <row role="data">
                            <cell role="data"><rs type="art" ref="ar0029">Bangor</rs></cell>
                            <cell role="data">0.</cell>
                            <cell role="data">8.</cell>
                            <cell role="data">0</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row role="data">
                            <cell role="data"><rs type="art" ref="ar0030">Owl</rs></cell>
                            <cell role="data">0</cell>
                            <cell role="data">2</cell>
                            <cell role="data">6</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row role="data">
                            <cell role="data"><rs type="art" ref="ar0031">Wynnstay</rs></cell>
                            <cell role="data">0</cell>
                            <cell role="data">5.</cell>
                            <cell role="data">0</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row role="data">
                            <cell role="data"><rs type="art" ref="ar0026">Arms</rs></cell>
                            <cell role="data">0</cell>
                            <cell role="data">1</cell>
                            <cell role="data">6</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row role="data">
                            <cell role="data"/>
                            <cell role="data"/>
                            <cell role="data">17.</cell>
                            <cell role="data">0</cell>
                        </row>
                    </table></p>
                <p>Things of more work he must have more for. single arms 14<hi rend="superscript">d</hi>. with quarters or coronets 18<hi rend="superscript">d</hi>. He shall
                    observe all <choice>
                        <abbr>y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi></abbr>
                        <expan>your</expan>
                    </choice> directions. </p>
                <p>I should not sleep very easy over such materials for a powder plot as you do.<note type="editorial">This may refer to anxieties about a repeat of the
                        Gordon Riots of June 1780, when London was subjected to six days of mob
                        rule, before Lord George Gordon (1751â€“93), widely seen as leader of the
                        protest, was arrested and charged with high treason. Hist P.</note> if you take a flight: the worst I wish that you &amp; yours
                    may light safe before my door. I am </p>
                <closer><salute>Dear Sir <lb/>most faithfully <choice>
                        <abbr>y<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi></abbr>
                        <expan>yours</expan>
                    </choice></salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232"><choice>
                                <abbr>Th.</abbr>
                                <expan>Thomas</expan>
                            </choice> Pennant.</persName></signed></closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p><bibl type="authorial"><title ref="bi0013">Snowdon</title></bibl>
                        arrived safely: &amp; will soon be made as fine as <persName ref="pe0014">moses</persName> can make it. <choice>
                            <abbr>Y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi></abbr>
                            <expan>your</expan>
                        </choice> parcel was sent long ago. &amp; I hope you sent for it to
                            <persName ref="pe0237">M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi> Pennant</persName>
                        <placeName ref="pl0798">upper grosvenour street</placeName></p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
